{"id":"fd95673253719076cc9913dc6b6292089606b86f","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1229596","title":"我开源了一个浏览器里管理 S3、R2 文件的工具，支持多种格式文件预览","site_name":"Info Flow","source":"V2EX (创意工作者社区)","byline":"hahahumble","excerpt":"分享创造 - @hahahumble - ![]( https://i.v2ex.co/UsW84cQ1.png)**项目地址**： https://storageui.dev/zh<br/>**Demo 地址**： https:","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div id=\"Main\">\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17901560\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a0c9/953b/65102_normal.png?m=1664639742\" alt=\"Phant0m\" data-uid=\"65102\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>1</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/Phant0m\">Phant0m</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-24 17:47:32 +08:00\">4h 49m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>有计划添加 webdav 支持吗?</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17902000\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4359/8882/484374_normal.png?m=1759030182\" alt=\"keer\" data-uid=\"484374\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>3</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/keer\">keer</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-24 20:59:51 +08:00\">1h 37m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>好东西。 一直用的桌面客户端管理 S3</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17902029\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4359/8882/484374_normal.png?m=1759030182\" alt=\"keer\" data-uid=\"484374\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>5</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/keer\">keer</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-24 21:16:49 +08:00\">1h 20m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <div><p>加个右键-复制链接的功能(如果用户填了公网访问的链接)</p><p>然后，在网页上添加的配置，只能在当前浏览器使用吗？ 是存 localstorage 的吗？</p></div>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17902042\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c56c/a46d/582969_normal.png?m=1784866872\" alt=\"hahahumble\" data-uid=\"582969\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>7</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/hahahumble\">hahahumble</a></strong> &#160; <div><p>OP</p></div>&#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-24 21:21:21 +08:00\">1h 16m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <div><p>@<a href=\"/member/keer\">keer</a> 好主意</p><p>是的，存在 localstorage 里的，环境变量里的配置可以在不同浏览器里使用</p></div>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n\n</div></DIV>","content_text":"1 Phant0m 4h 49m ago 有计划添加 webdav 支持吗? 3 keer 1h 37m ago 好东西。 一直用的桌面客户端管理 S3 5 keer 1h 20m ago 加个右键-复制链接的功能(如果用户填了公网访问的链接)然后，在网页上添加的配置，只能在当前浏览器使用吗？ 是存 localstorage 的吗？ 7 hahahumble OP 1h 16m ago @keer 好主意是的，存在 localstorage 里的，环境变量里的配置可以在不同浏览器里使用","fetched_at":"2026-07-24T14:38:17.842Z","ok":true}